name: Glitches of Evil
description:
A dark, glitch-filled, black and white collage of different versions of the scariest personification of evil I’ve seen in a photo.

This piece was created to celebrate reaching 666 followers on Twitter.

3606x4957 pixel PNG

Minted August 17th, 2021. Verify via Twitter account @tormential and/or Instagram account @_tormential_ and/or tormential.tez
